            "5": "Triggering an elemental reaction increases the character's ATK by 32% for 12s, and when a Stellar-Conduct/Stellar Swirl reaction is triggered, Stellar-Conduct/Stellar Swirl DMG is also increased by 32% for 12s. The aforementioned effects can still trigger even when the equipping character is not on the field."
